window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>As new enemies close in, Clay Carradine must master his magic.</b></p> <p>Having saved Thea from being enslaved by an evil sorcerer, Clay hoped his problems were over. Yet his victory has drawn more interest, not less.</p> <p>As he tries to build a life with Thea and Gemma, the lovely barista who helped him save Thea, sorcerers from other worlds seek Clay’s power for themselves.</p> <p>With the help of Salem, an arcane bounty hunter, and Eleandra, a sorceress from another world, Clay must learn to defend himself and those he loves before it’s too late.</p>"; 
